  <scopecontent id="aspace_f435a5a463a66a4bba14420dbeb5921b">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>This collection documents Tobias' professional career as a female writer involved in the food industry in New York City during the late 20th century. Materials include recipes, menus, print publications, clippings, food and wine event packets, business cards, financial and apartment contract records, writings, and a toy truck commemorating George Duboeuf's annual Beaujolais Nouveau.</p>  </scopecontent>
